articles.description: Kavion Pippen scored 21 points with eight rebounds and four blocks and Southern Illinois defeated Bradley 74-57 on Sunday to take over sole possession of second place in the Missouri Valley Conference.
articles.headline: Southern Illinois alone in 2nd in MVC after win over Bradley

articles.description: Upset Saturday in the Big 12 saw four of the league's top five teams lose. No. 19 West Virginia must shake the sting of blowing a late six-point lead at home against Oklahoma State.
articles.headline: No. 19 West Virginia looking to bounce back vs. TCU

articles.description: Bearcats senior Kyle Washington drops 17 points and leads Cincinnati to a 76-51 win over SMU, extending Cincy's perfect streak in the American Athletic Conference.
articles.headline: Cincinnati gets road win over SMU

images.caption: Bearcats senior Kyle Washington drops 17 points and leads Cincinnati to a 76-51 win over SMU, extending Cincy's perfect streak in the American Athletic Conference.

articles.description: Kyle Washington had 17 points with eight rebounds and No. 6 Cincinnati remained undefeated in American Athletic Conference play, stretching its overall winning streak to 16 games with a 76-51 victory over short-handed SMU on Sunday.
articles.headline: No. 6 Cincinnati routs short-handed SMU for 16th win in row

images.caption: Bearcats senior Kyle Washington drops 17 points and leads Cincinnati to a 76-51 win over SMU, extending Cincy's perfect streak in the American Athletic Conference.

articles.headline: No. 21 Tar Heels finish tough stretch against Notre Dame

videos.description: Jalen Hudson waste no time and hits 3-pointer early for the Gators.
videos.headline: Florida's Hudson drains pull up 3-pointer

videos.description: Egor Koulechov uses the pump fake to get around the defender and makes the layup plus the foul.
videos.headline: Florida's Koulechov makes tough and-1 layup

videos.description: Chris Chiozza gets to the loose ball and makes the no-look pass to an open Deaundrae Ballard for the dunk.
videos.headline: Florida's Chiozza makes great pass to Ballard for dunk

videos.description: Grayson Allen finds the cutting Trevon Duval who makes the nice one-handed layup.
videos.headline: Duke's Allen passes to Duval for nice up-and-under layup

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III is staying hot early and showing off all parts of his game in the first half.
videos.headline: Duke's Bagley shows his full game by hitting layup and 3-pointer

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III misses the shot but is able to get the rebound and score the basket.
videos.headline: Duke's Bagley finishes his own miss

videos.description: Florida head coach Mike White says he has no idea on how to stop Duke's Marvin Bagley III in the 2nd half.
videos.headline: White pleased with Florida's offense in 1st half

videos.description: Jalen Hudson grabs the board and goes all the way down the floor for the layup.
videos.headline: Florida's Hudson gets the rebound, goes coast-to-coast for score

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III with the huge block and hustles to the other end for the lay-in.
videos.headline: Bagley gets the big block and runs the floor to score layup

videos.description: Javin Delaurier picks Jalen Hudson's pocket for the steal, goes the length of the court and slams it home.
videos.headline: Duke's DeLaurier gets the steal, hammers home dunk

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III loses the ball and Florida's  Deaundrae Ballard hits the jumper at the other end.
videos.headline: Bagley turnover leads to Ballard jumper

videos.description: Grayson Allen uses the fake to get an opening and hits the 3-pointer to cut Florida's lead to just 3.
videos.headline: Grayson Allen pumps and drains big 3-pointer

videos.description: Wendell Carter Jr. finds Marvin Bagely III down low and he goes up strong to score.
videos.headline: Marvin Bagley III gets the pass and finishes the layup

videos.description: The Gators are unable to get a decent shot attempt as time expires, sealing the Blue Devils' 87-84 win.
videos.headline: Florida can't get shot off, fall to Duke

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III loves the way his team did not give up and fought to overcome a double-digit deficit to beat Florida.
videos.headline: Marvin Bagley praises Duke's effort in comeback win

videos.description: Jay Bilas and Dan Shulman breakdown the ways Marvin Bagley III dominated for Duke this tournament, especially against Florida.
videos.headline: Marvin Bagley III powers Duke in PK80 Invitational

videos.description: The No. 1 Blue Devils, behind a 30-point, 15-rebound performance from Marvin Bagley III, close the game out on a 15-2 run to defeat the No. 7 Gators 87-84.
videos.headline: Duke rallies to beat Florida

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III scores 30 points and adds 15 boards as the No. 1 Blue Devils charge back late to knock off the No. 7 Gators 87-84 to win the "Motion Bracket" of the PK80 Invitational.
videos.headline: Bagley sparks Duke comeback over Florida
